    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have resistance to fire damage while you hold this staff.</p><p>The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.6HSESlJ472aQngrP]{burning hands}</em> (1 charge), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.VYvD59yJYefhAwOI]{fireball}</em> (3 charges), or <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.xOthSJ1mF0Qpe9DM]{wall of fire}</em> (4 charges).</p><p>The staff regains [[/r 1d6 + 4]] expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff blackens, crumbles into cinders, and is destroyed.</p>",
      "source": {
